            <li>Bihar has a rich legacy of education and research, with its roots tracing back to ancient times. The state was home to the world-renowned Nalanda University, one of the oldest universities in the world, which attracted scholars from across Asia. Today, Bihar continues this tradition with institutions like Patna University, one of the oldest universities in India, and other prominent educational centers such as the Indian Institute of Technology (IIT) Patna and National Institute of Technology (NIT) Patna.</li>
